Package org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.transform

Class GeoProjection

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.transform.GeoProjection
Direct Known Subclasses:
LazyGeoProjection, Wgs84Projection
public abstract class GeoProjection extends Object
Provides methods to transform geographic coordinates from and to cartesian coordinates.
